PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FResearchers are encouraging the NHS to
OL,7,Fadopt new miscarriage prevention
OL,8,Fmethods after a trial said 10,000
OL,9,Fcould be prevented each year, ITV News
OL,10,FCorrespondent Stacey Foster reports
OL,12,FMore than 10,000 miscarriages could be
OL,13,Fprevented every year by giving women
OL,14,Ffollow-up care after their first
OL,15,Fmiscarriage, according to a new report
OL,16,Fby pregnancy and baby charity Tommy's.
OL,18,FAt the moment, NHS guidelines mean
OL,19,Ftests will be offered after three
OL,20,Fpregnancy losses in England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FThe charity is calling for the NHS to
OL,7,Fadopt its "Graded Model of Miscarriage
OL,8,FCare" nationwide, following a pilot by
OL,9,Fresearchers at Tommy's National Centre
OL,10,Ffor Miscarriage Research and
OL,11,FBirmingham Women's Hospital, showing
OL,12,Fimproved outcomes for women and
OL,13,Ffamilies.
OL,15,FThe study found the enhanced care
OL,16,Fpackage can be achieved "without
OL,17,Fsignificant additional workload for
OL,18,FNHS teams" in existing Early Pregnancy
OL,19,FUnits in hospitals across the country,
OL,20,Fsparing thousands of families
OL,21,Fadditional trauma.
OL,26,@oD@KOUpD@EO]xD@YOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FThe pilot at Birmingham Women's
OL,7,FHospital saw women offered a one-to-
OL,8,Fone consultation with a specialist
OL,9,Fnurse after their first loss to
OL,10,Fdiscuss health before conception and
OL,11,Fduring pregnancy.
OL,13,FAfter two miscarriages, patients would
OL,14,Fbe offered tests for anaemia and
OL,15,Fabnormal thyroid function.
OL,17,FIf they go on to have a third, women
OL,18,Fwould be offered the current standard
OL,19,FNHS care and a referral to a recurrent
OL,20,Fmiscarriage clinic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FProfessor Arri Coomarasamy, director
OL,7,Fof Tommy's National Centre for
OL,8,FMiscarriage Research, said: "If the
OL,9,Fgraded model were implemented across
OL,10,Fthe UK, our study indicates it could
OL,11,Fprevent around 10,075 miscarriages
OL,12,Fevery year.
OL,14,F"That's more than 10,000 families
OL,15,Fbringing their babies home instead of
OL,16,Fsuffering the trauma of a pregnancy
OL,17,Floss."
OL,26,@pD@]OUvD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FThe trial in Birmingham has now ended
OL,7,Fand so women arriving at the Early
OL,8,FPregnancy unit in Birmingham can no
OL,9,Flonger be offered additional support.
OL,11,F"That's the heartbreaking thing," one
OL,12,Fof the nurses told me.
OL,14,FThe trial included 203 women with a
OL,15,Fhistory of one or more miscarriages
OL,16,Fwho were given early intervention,
OL,17,Falong with 203 who had the usual care.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FOf the women who had the graded model
OL,7,Fof care, 86% had one or more factors
OL,8,Fdetected that could increase their
OL,9,Frisk of future miscarriages, compared
OL,10,Fto 58% in the group who had standard
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,FAccording to the study, women treated
OL,14,Fusing the graded model had a 4% lower
OL,15,Frisk of a pregnancy after miscarriage
OL,16,Fending in another loss.
OL,18,FFay Wickett, one of the participants
OL,19,Fin the study, previously suffered two
OL,20,Fmiscarriages and was referred to
OL,21,FTommy's.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,F"I'm so grateful the big change with
OL,7,Fthis model is that usually a lady
OL,8,Fwould have to have three miscarriages
OL,9,Fbefore they would be able to access an
OL,10,Fappointment with a consultant, but I
OL,11,Fwas included after two," she said.
OL,12,F"I'm so grateful that they looked at
OL,13,Fmy bloods, looked at my health and
OL,14,Fsupported me."
OL,16,FShe received additional reassurance
OL,17,Fscans while she was pregnant to ensure
OL,18,Fher baby was developing as expected.
OL,20,FMyleene Klass, who is an Ambassador
OL,21,Ffor Tommy's, joined us on the ward.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FThe singer and broadcaster has been
OL,7,Fcampaigning for improved care for
OL,8,Fwomen who have a history of
OL,9,Fmiscarriage after herself experiencing
OL,10,Ffour devastating losses before her son
OL,11,Fwas born.
OL,13,FShe explained that she was due to meet
OL,14,Fthe Health Secretary, Wes Streeting,
OL,15,Fon April 27 to discuss the findings of
OL,16,Fthe study, but "he cancelled".
OL,18,FKlass showed me the emails from his
OL,19,Fteam apologising for a diary-clash and
OL,20,Fsuggesting new dates.
OL,26,@xD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529103
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FShe does not care about the meeting.
OL,7,FLike many women, she just wants
OL,8,Fsomeone to do something to improve
OL,9,Foutcomes.
OL,11,F"Ultimately the meeting is one thing
OL,12,Fand it would have been nice to discuss
OL,13,Fthe findings as they are essential to
OL,14,Fmaking sure the 250,000 women who are
OL,15,Flosing babies every year feel like
OL,16,Fthey are looked after," she said.
OL,18,F"These are actual lives that we're
OL,19,Fplaying with."
OL,26,@sD@AOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529104
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FKlass continued: "It's cruel, we're
OL,7,Fmaking the women in this country
OL,8,Fsuffer needlessly.
OL,10,F"There are women who are miscarrying
OL,11,Fat work, miscarrying on toilet floors,
OL,12,Fmiscarrying in their homes not knowing
OL,13,Fwhere to go and I cannot believe that
OL,14,Fin today's day and age that we believe
OL,15,Fthat is okay.
OL,17,F"We are torturing women."
OL,26,@nD@ROUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529104
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FShe added: "My question to our health
OL,7,Fsecretary and our politicians is, if
OL,8,Fyou take baby loss seriously as you
OL,9,Fsay you do and you think it is as
OL,10,Funacceptable as it is, why are you not
OL,11,Facting on it?"
OL,13,FTommy's experts say one year of
OL,14,Fimplementing the Graded Model of
OL,15,FMiscarriage Care could save the NHS
OL,16,Fover #40 million across the UK, based
OL,17,Fon preventing 10,075 miscarriages.
OL,19,FThese estimates include reduced NHS
OL,20,Fcosts, fewer productivity losses and
OL,21,Fwider societal impacts.
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529104
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FScotland has already begun integrating
OL,7,Fthe model into its miscarriage care
OL,8,Fpathway.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FTommy's is now urging policymakers in
OL,16,FEngland, Wales and Northern Ireland to
OL,17,Ffollow suit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777529104
OL,3,CEarly care scheme could prevent 'more
OL,4,Cthan 10,000 miscarriages a year'
OL,6,FThe government has committed, through
OL,7,Fits Women's Health Strategy for
OL,8,FEngland, to review the findings and
OL,9,Fconsider wider NHS implementation.
OL,11,FBaroness Merron, parliamentary under-
OL,12,Fsecretary of state at the Department
OL,13,Fof Health and Social Care, welcomed
OL,14,Fthe study and said its findings "will
OL,15,Fbe carefully considered".
OL,17,FShe added: "Pregnancy and baby loss
OL,18,Fcan have a devastating impact on women
OL,19,Fand families, who too often feel they
OL,20,Fhave been left without the care and
OL,21,Fsupport they need.
OL,26,@vD@aOUwD@XO]yD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
